reports.missionName: Let me out, what you see is not the same person as me. My life's a lie. I'm not who you're looking. Let me out. Set me free. I'm really old. This isn't me. My real body is slowly dieing in a vat. Is anybody listening? Can anyone understand? Stop looking at me like that and actually help me. Help me. Help me I'm gunna die.
He's not a hot girl. He can't just bail on his life and set up shop in someone else's.
That's the difference between you and me, Morty. I never go back to the carpet store.
